eventName: How to Crack Top Companies Off Campus in 2022 ? | Tier 3 College to Walmart
eventDescription: Cracking top MNCs for a tier 3 college student is a tough way, so in this podcast, we will be having Hinkal Jain with us, who recently joined Walmart as SDE 2. She will be sharing her experience and tips for clearing the interview, also start your preparation beforehand.

eventName: How to win Hackathons like a PRO | Garvit Chouhan
eventDescription: This video focuses around what are the key points which are required to keep in mind during a hackathon. How to think, plan and execute upon a certain idea. How to bring your solution to the top of the list in the Hackathon and also make that a winning solution.
